Transamerica Corp said its boardauthorized the repurchase of up to 2.2 mln shares of itsoutstanding stock in addition to the 1.5 mln shares previouslyauthorized.    The company has 72.7 mln shares outstanding.    It said the reacquired 2.2 mln shares will be used to meetexcercise requirements for its stock options plans, while thepreviously approved 1.5 mln shares may be used for employeebenefit plan or other corporate purposes. Reuter&#3;